Package: easyNRD
Title: Tidy Tools for HCUP Nationwide Readmissions Database Workflows
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Ali", "Salman", email = "alisalman.et.al@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A tidy, DuckDB-backed toolkit for Healthcare Cost and Utilization
    Project Nationwide Readmissions Database (HCUP-NRD) data. 'easyNRD'
    provides a discharge-level workflow to ingest parquet data, prepare NRD
    timing fields, flag diagnosis and procedure conditions, link first
    qualifying readmissions, export parquet results, and instantiate survey
    designs for weighted analysis.
